approximation algorithm to solve the revenue maximization problem\nwith provable theoretical guarantee on the revenue gap. We conduct extensive\nexperiments on four public datasets to validate the superior performance of our\nproposed algorithms.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 19 Jun 2021 11:19:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-22"}
