Model-independent limits on the product of the cross section, signal\nacceptance, and branching fraction to the W$\\gamma$ channel are set for minimum\nW$\\gamma$ mass thresholds between 1.5 and 8.0 TeV.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 19 Jun 2021 14:54:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 4 Feb 2022 13:33:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-07"}
